हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/CSCYXg
show.description: Backstabbed By My Sisters follows Aaditya, a scarred orphan rescued by three sisters who raise him as their own. Together, they build a billion-dollar empire—until one fateful night, they betray him and leave him for dead. But Aaditya survives, reborn with the divine power of the mystical Trinetra Stone. As he rises from the ashes, he must confront love, revenge, and destiny to take back everything that was stolen. A gripping tale of betrayal, rebirth, and unstoppable justice. Watch Now !
